title: QA Analyst
description: Software QA Testers ensure the quality of software products by designing and executing test cases, identifying defects, and reporting issues to developers. They play a critical role in ensuring software reliability and functionality.
responsibilities: Perform manual testing of software applications
and report issues. Create and execute test cases and test plans. Collaborate with developers to resolve defects.
